♪Holding hands silently
as flowers fall and winds rise♪

00:00:10.432 --> 00:00:13.536
♪Dark tresses cascade like mountains.
Dreams intertwine♪

00:00:13.536 --> 00:00:17.856
♪Painting realms, clouds in palm,
my brushwork for you♪

00:00:18.048 --> 00:00:22.112
♪Light and shadow overlap
my name across time and space♪

00:00:22.272 --> 00:00:25.960
♪Across starry rivers,
I chase dreams afar♪

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:30.624
♪Arms spread wide,
falling through heaven and earth♪

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:33.280
♪The rhythm of breath and heartbeat♪

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:38.464
♪A meeting of the souls♪

00:00:39.168 --> 00:00:43.424
♪Through shifting seas and lands,
I'd know you still♪

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:47.800
♪Eyes bright as moonlit skies,
untouched by worldly dust♪

00:00:48.032 --> 00:00:51.680
♪Smiling gazes write eternity♪

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:56.768
=The Crush=

00:00:57.235 --> 00:00:59.721
=Episode 13=
(Getting Divorced and Imprisoned)

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:01.920
Today, there was

00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:04.480
a scandal of an adultery among us women,

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:06.520
which brings disgrace to our family.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.240
I failed to manage the household well.

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:11.720
I failed the ancestors
of our family.

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.320
By family rules,
I must accept punishment.

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.200
Madam, you are

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.320
not the one at fault.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.400
I'm not the one at fault.

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:26.160
Then who is it at fault?

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:29.216
Cuicui.

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:33.880
Cuicui, you are Madam Li's maid.

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:36.120
She left her seat without permission

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:37.680
and stayed alone with a man,

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.440
which brings disgrace to our family.

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:40.720
Who is it at fault?

00:01:41.320 --> 00:01:42.680
I apologize, Madam.

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:44.680
Are you admitting your mistake?

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:47.200
Think it over.

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:48.760
By family rules,

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:51.720
eighty lashes for those
who bring disgrace to our family.

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:55.648
Ning An.

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:58.520
You grew up with Zixuan.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:01:59.960
Tell me.

00:02:00.920 --> 00:02:02.880
What Madam Li did today

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:04.680
has brought disgrace to our family.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.960
Who is it at fault?

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:13.280
Since you all refuse to speak,

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:16.200
then you shall bear punishment for her.

00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:18.240
Guards! Eighty lashes for each.

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.200
Show no mercy.

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:20.256
How dare you!

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:21.984
Young Master.

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:23.424
- Young Master! Madam Li!
- Miss!

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:27.800
- Get up.
- Who dares to get up!

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:29.160
Do as I say. Get up.

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:31.392
It's alright.

00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:34.280
Wei Xiaotang.

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:35.720
What you did today

00:02:35.720 --> 00:02:38.760
has brought disgrace to our family.

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:40.720
I demand an explanation!

00:02:41.880 --> 00:02:42.848
Mother!

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.600
This matter hasn't been settled yet.

00:02:44.880 --> 00:02:46.720
Why are you so eager to be the judge?

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:48.720
Does the disgrace to our family

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:50.400
bring you joy?

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:51.960
A man and a woman

00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:53.200
stayed alone in a room

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:54.520
in disheveled clothing.

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:56.880
All people from Haiqing
tea estates witnessed it!

00:02:57.160 --> 00:02:58.640
How can you

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.480
still deny it?

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:02.840
I went to meet Hassan

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:04.320
to discuss business.

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:05.680
Moreover, I sent Cuicui

00:03:06.040 --> 00:03:07.360
to fetch Zixuan to join us.

00:03:07.640 --> 00:03:08.720
Let me ask her.

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:10.640
Cuicui.

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:12.320
When you to fetched Zixuan,

00:03:12.520 --> 00:03:14.360
did someone hold you back?

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:16.360
Miss.

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:18.080
I was going to find Mr. Zixuan,

00:03:18.320 --> 00:03:20.200
but Madam Tang stopped me suddenly

00:03:20.440 --> 00:03:21.920
and told me to fetch water instead.

00:03:23.600 --> 00:03:24.600
I see now.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:27.320
You are such a show-off person,

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:28.680
yet didn't take any credit

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:31.600
and let tea merchants
constantly toast me.

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:34.000
Did you do it on purpose?

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:37.040
You and your maid

00:03:37.400 --> 00:03:39.080
have ruined our family's reputation.

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:40.352
And now you try to act innocent

00:03:40.352 --> 00:03:41.280
and slander me?

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:43.400
If I don't punish you now,

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.520
I'm afraid our family
will lose all discipline!

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:52.000
Zixuan, she claimed innocence,

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:53.400
do you believe her?

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:55.040
If they were truly

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:56.600
discussing business,

00:03:56.600 --> 00:03:59.000
then why did you beat that Persian man?

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.208
I beat him

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:04.520
just to protect my wife.

00:04:04.704 --> 00:04:05.600
Mother,

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:07.120
if my wife was being harassed,

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.360
how could I not be furious?

00:04:08.880 --> 00:04:09.856
Zixuan.

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:12.280
You've spent too much time
with bad woman,

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:14.040
and now you are also acting rudely.

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:16.840
Can't you even distinguish
right from wrong anymore?

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.080
The women of our family

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.520
have always valued dignity above life.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:25.680
If you defend her,

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.640
you're pushing all the women here

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:29.000
into a corner.

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:31.640
What do you want me to do then?

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:33.960
Immediately write
a letter of divorce to Wei Xiaotang

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:35.840
and expel her from the family!

00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:37.960
It is none of your business.

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:39.440
It has nothing

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:40.440
to do with you.

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.720
It's come to this.

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:46.080
It's not for you to decide
whether you divorce her or not.

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:49.880
Wei Xiaotang
has violated marital virtues,

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:51.480
bringing disgrace to our family.

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:52.760
By the family rules,

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:54.600
she'll receive whipping punishment

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:55.920
and then be expelled.

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:57.640
Guards, bring me the whip.

00:04:57.640 --> 00:04:58.800
Who dares to do that?

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:01.640
As the eldest son of the Li family,

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:02.760
you have

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.120
no say here.

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:05.984
You!

00:05:06.920 --> 00:05:07.960
Enough!

00:05:11.320 --> 00:05:12.320
Father.

00:05:13.216 --> 00:05:14.120
Mr. Wei.

00:05:14.120 --> 00:05:15.240
Come on.

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:16.480
Father!

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:17.600
Mr. Wei.

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:19.920
Escort Xiaotang back to the Wei Manor.

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:21.360
Why?

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:22.280
Let's go, Miss.

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:24.440
Can't we talk this out here?

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:25.560
- Xiaotang!
- Father!

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:26.920
- Miss!
- Why go back?

00:05:26.920 --> 00:05:27.840
Mr. Wei.

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:28.880
You got me wrong.

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:30.400
If you can't protect

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:31.600
my daughter well,

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:32.920
I'll find someone else

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:34.240
who can do so.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:35.600
Also,

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:38.000
it's not you divorcing her,

00:05:38.520 --> 00:05:40.640
but us disowning you!

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.400
Let's go.

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:43.936
Mr. Wei.

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:58.688
Xiaotang.

00:05:59.760 --> 00:06:00.840
Now,

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.400
rest assured.

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:03.880
I've made it clear

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:05.960
that anyone spreading rumors about you

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.640
will have their lips sewn shut.

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:11.080
Just live well,

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:13.160
eat well, and drink well.

00:06:13.184 --> 00:06:14.160
If bored,

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:16.560
go buy cosmetics and jewelry.

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.080
If you prefer staying at home,

00:06:19.400 --> 00:06:22.120
have those merchants of cosmetics

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:23.840
and garments

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:25.640
come to us

00:06:25.880 --> 00:06:26.960
with their best wares.

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:28.200
You can pick them here.

00:06:28.360 --> 00:06:29.720
I've done nothing wrong,

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.680
so I fear no gossip.

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:32.720
Well done!

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:34.240
You're my daughter, after all.

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:35.680
Never be coward.

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:38.120
This comes from me.

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:43.240
Let me make this clear.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.360
Since you've divorced Zixuan,

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:46.600
in the future,

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:48.440
if you don't want to remarry,

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:50.920
then live with me.

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:52.000
I'll support you lifelong,

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:53.320
ensuring your comfort.

00:06:53.880 --> 00:06:55.480
If you want to remarry,

00:06:55.640 --> 00:06:57.480
I'll gather all eligible bachelors

00:06:57.480 --> 00:06:59.480
from Haiqing Town and nearby counties

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.680
for you.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:02.440
No, Father.

00:07:02.840 --> 00:07:04.360
I must return to the Li family

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:06.440
and make the Top Tea with Zixuan.

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:11.480
He let Madam Tang scold you!

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:13.320
Why return to him?

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:14.760
Just stay here.

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:15.904
Don't meet him.

00:07:23.720 --> 00:07:25.560
This won't do!

00:07:30.932 --> 00:07:34.080
(Wei Manor)

00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:36.928
Mr. Wei.

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:38.400
I want to see Xiaotang.

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:43.488
What?

00:07:44.320 --> 00:07:45.376
No way!

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.800
It's the divorce letter.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:48.640
It's registered with the yamen.

00:07:49.200 --> 00:07:50.480
From now on,

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:52.800
our families are severed.

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:55.600
From now on,
I'm no longer your father-in-law.

00:07:55.760 --> 00:07:57.680
And Xiaotang is no longer your wife.

00:07:58.880 --> 00:07:59.920
Mr. Wei.

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:00.800
You misunderstand me.

00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:02.120
No matter what happened,

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:03.400
I never want to divorce her.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:06.160
Please let me see Xiaotang.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:07.880
What for?

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:09.440
In your family,

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:10.280
she is nothing

00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:12.840
but a woman who got accused of adultery.

00:08:13.024 --> 00:08:14.040
Mr. Wei.

00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:15.240
I'll uncover the truth

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:16.280
and clear Xiaotang's name.

00:08:16.480 --> 00:08:18.240
I won't let her bear this shame.

00:08:18.640 --> 00:08:19.600
Fine.

00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:22.240
When you've cleared Xiaotang's name,

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:23.440
then come to us.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:24.960
You may leave.

00:08:25.880 --> 00:08:28.000
Mr. Li, please.

00:09:00.520 --> 00:09:02.600
Young Master, everything is ready.

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:04.400
Madam Li will meet you
at the arch bridge.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:07.400
Well done.

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:08.960
You'll get a bonus this month.

00:09:09.400 --> 00:09:10.368
Thank you, Young Master.

00:09:10.624 --> 00:09:11.520
Right.

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:12.360
One more thing.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.520
We've located that Persian man.

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.440
A man from trade caravan
spotted a Persian man

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:17.760
at the suburban post station.

00:09:17.880 --> 00:09:19.400
His appearance resembles Hassan's.

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:20.544
Let's go.

00:09:42.920 --> 00:09:44.680
I spared your life that day

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:46.480
to make you

00:09:46.520 --> 00:09:48.120
clear my wife's name.

00:09:49.360 --> 00:09:51.600
Mr. Li, Madam Li

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:52.520
came to me that day.

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:56.800
If you dare slander my wife again,

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.440
I'll kill you now!

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:01.000
Mr. Li.

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:01.888
Please...

00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:03.200
Please calm down.

00:10:04.280 --> 00:10:05.800
Someone told me

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:08.400
to lure Miss Xiaotang to the attic.

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:11.640
Who told you to do so?

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:13.760
I don't know.

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:15.320
He didn't show his face.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:25.880
We foreign merchants

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:27.160
need travel permits

00:10:27.232 --> 00:10:28.280
to move

00:10:28.280 --> 00:10:30.640
freely here.

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:33.960
Without them to prove our identity,
we can't go anywhere.

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:35.440
I'll give it to you,

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:37.680
and you can summon me anytime

00:10:38.040 --> 00:10:38.880
to test for you.

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:41.800
Go to the yamen tomorrow morning

00:10:41.800 --> 00:10:43.560
and clarify
the Zhenxiu Restaurant incident

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:45.600
to clear my wife's name.

00:11:02.200 --> 00:11:04.280
Uncle, why are you here?

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:05.720
Why am I here?

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.120
I came here for you.

00:11:08.920 --> 00:11:10.112
Right, sister.

00:11:10.112 --> 00:11:11.680
Remember those Persian friends I made?

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:14.840
They gave me all sorts of exotic items,

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:16.760
including those gadgets Zimo is holding.

00:11:17.160 --> 00:11:19.600
Uncle, you have Persian friends?

00:11:20.256 --> 00:11:21.120
By the way,

00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:24.080
are your foreign friends reliable?

00:11:24.800 --> 00:11:27.240
This plan can't fail.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.560
Don't worry, sister.

00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:30.040
Everything has been arranged.

00:11:36.080 --> 00:11:38.720
The Li family will belong to Zimo alone.

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:40.240
You're finally acting like an uncle.

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:41.480
Of course.

00:11:41.747 --> 00:11:44.960
(Tea)

00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:46.800
Ning An told us to wait here,

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:47.680
but

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:49.400
it looks like it's going to rain.

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:51.640
Young Master Zixuan must be held up.

00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:52.760
He's not coming.

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:54.640
He invited me to come,

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:55.640
yet he has been late.

00:11:55.640 --> 00:11:56.512
Xiaotang.

00:12:27.880 --> 00:12:29.280
You're late, you know?

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:32.560
I got held up on the road.

00:12:35.720 --> 00:12:36.680
About that day...

00:12:36.680 --> 00:12:37.600
Xiaotang.

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:39.840
I believe you.

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:16.800
It's raining.

00:13:28.840 --> 00:13:29.920
Let's go.

00:14:57.520 --> 00:14:58.680
It rains so heavily.

00:15:02.760 --> 00:15:03.800
With this downpour,

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.160
I couldn't go back today.

00:15:05.520 --> 00:15:06.432
Indeed.

00:15:07.840 --> 00:15:10.480
Cuicui told me
Wei Manor has strict curfews.

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:13.400
The gate closes at the hour of Xu.

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:15.760
You probably can't go back either.

00:15:16.920 --> 00:15:17.920
Indeed.

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:19.600
This rain

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:21.280
won't stop soon.

00:15:24.560 --> 00:15:26.160
Maybe when the rain eases a little,

00:15:26.560 --> 00:15:28.360
we'll find an inn to stay.

00:15:34.880 --> 00:15:36.000
What?

00:15:38.680 --> 00:15:41.080
Li Zixuan, you want
to stay in a room with me?

00:15:41.248 --> 00:15:42.432
What's the problem?

00:15:44.360 --> 00:15:45.880
Then why do it secretly?

00:15:45.920 --> 00:15:47.320
You are

00:15:47.480 --> 00:15:48.840
my legitimate wife.

00:15:49.040 --> 00:15:50.280
Why can't we go home?

00:15:50.440 --> 00:15:51.960
Why stay in an inn then?

00:15:52.920 --> 00:15:54.144
Mr. Li.

00:15:56.040 --> 00:15:57.120
Persian merchants reported

00:15:57.520 --> 00:15:58.600
their companion

00:15:58.600 --> 00:15:59.760
named Hassan has been missing.

00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:01.440
We suspect you killed him.

00:16:01.800 --> 00:16:04.160
We need to take you
to the yamen for questioning.